<% content_for :title, "@piertutor | Home" %>
<% content_for :meta_description, "Camionista, Content Creator, Volvo Trucks Ambassador" %>

<%# HERO SECTION %>
<section class="relative h-[95vh] overflow-hidden lg:h-[95vh]">
  <!-- Image element positioned behind -->
  <img src="<%= asset_path("hero.webp") %>" alt="piertutor in posa davanti al suo camion" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-[50%_100%] scale-110 lg:scale-130 lg:origin-left"/>
  
  <!-- Dark overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/20 to-black/90 md:bg-gradient-to-l md:from-black/50 md:to-black/90"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-8 relative z-10 text-white pb-16 h-full flex flex-col justify-end lg:justify-center lg:px-0">
    <h1 class="archivo text-xl mb-2 lg:text-4xl lg:mb-4">@piertutor</h1>
    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-4 lg:text-6xl lg:mb-8 lg:max-w-screen-md">Camionista, Content Creator, Volvo Trucks Ambassador</h2>
    <div class="flex gap-3">
      <a href="#about"><button class="translate-x-[2px] px-4 py-2 bg-brand text-black border-1 border-black shadow-[-4px_4px_0_0_#FFF] transition-all transition-150 hover:translate-x-[-4px] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:shadow-none hover:cursor-pointer active:translate-x-[-4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-none">Scopri chi sono</button></a>
      <a href="#contact"><button class="translate-x-[2px] px-4 py-2 bg-white text-black border-1 border-black shadow-[-4px_4px_0_0_#FFF] transition-all transition-150 hover:translate-x-[-4px] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:shadow-none hover:cursor-pointer active:translate-x-[-4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-none">Contattami</button></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# HELLO SECTION %>
<section id="about" class="relative min-h-[95vh] lg:min-h-[95vh] lg:flex lg:flex-col lg:justify-center">
  <img src="<%= asset_path("about.webp") %>" alt="piertutor in svezia per uno shooting con i nuovi volvo aero" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-[51%_25%]"/>
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto w-full py-24 px-8 relative z-10 text-white flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-between lg:px-0 lg:gap-24 lg:items-center">
    <div class="lg:max-w-screen-md">
      <h2 class="text-4xl mb-4 lg:text-6xl lg:mb-8 lg:max-w-screen-md">Ciao, Sono Piertutor</h1>
      <p class="lg:text-lg">Mi chiamo Pierantonio De Piccoli e nel web sono anche conosciuto come Piertutor. Sono un camionista con oltre 20 anni di esperienza, ma la strada è solo l'inizio della mia storia. Dal 2019 racconto le mie giornate dietro al volante, condividendo i momenti più emozionanti: dalle manovre più impegnative ai panorami mozzafiato. Oggi, decine di migliaia di persone mi seguono su Instagram, Facebook, TikTok e YouTube e milioni di spettatori al mese si uniscono alle mie avventure.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-start items-center gap-4 mt-12 lg:flex-col lg:gap-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
        <span class="text-5xl archivo-black lg:text-7xl">50M+</span>
        <span class="lg:text-xl">view mensili</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
        <span class="text-5xl archivo-black lg:text-7xl">50k+</span>
        <span class="lg:text-xl">followers</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
        <span class="text-5xl archivo-black lg:text-7xl">20+</span>
        <span class="lg:text-xl">anni al volante</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# SECTIONS %>
<section class="border-t-2 border-brand sticky top-0 min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col justify-end overflow-hidden">
  <img src="<%= asset_path("selfie.webp") %>" alt="selfie di piertutor" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-[50%_50%]"/>
  
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-black/50 to-black/90 absolute inset-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto w-full py-12 px-8 relative z-10 text-white lg:px-0 lg:py-32">
    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-4 lg:text-6xl lg:mb-8">Storia</h1>
    <p class="lg:max-w-screen-md lg:text-lg">Dal 2019, documento la mia vita da camionista e le meraviglie che incontro lungo il cammino. Oggi collaboro con molti brand, affrontando temi fondamentali come la sicurezza alla guida, l'efficienza e la sostenibilità. È incredibile pensare che oggi oltre 2 milioni di persone guardano i miei video, e che ogni giorno i miei fan mi salutano quando mi vedono passare con il mio camion.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-t-2 border-brand sticky top-6 min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col justify-end overflow-hidden lg:top-12">
  <img src="<%= asset_path("focus.webp") %>" alt="selfie di piertutor" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-[10%_50%]"/>
  
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-black/50 to-black/90 absolute inset-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto w-full py-12 px-8 relative z-10 text-white lg:px-0 lg:py-32">
    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-4 lg:text-6xl lg:mb-8">Missione</h1>
    <p class="text lg:max-w-screen-md lg:text-lg">Il mio obiettivo sui social è creare un legame autentico con chi mi segue, offrendo intrattenimento e divertimento, ma sempre con un occhio di riguardo alla sicurezza sulla strada. Realizzo video dinamici, ripresi da più angolazioni e con telecamere diverse, per portarti contenuti originali e distintivi nel mondo dei camion.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-t-2 border-brand sticky top-12 min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col justify-start items-center overflow-hidden lg:top-24">
  <img src="<%= asset_path("group.webp") %>" alt="selfie di piertutor" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-[50%_50%]"/>
  
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-black/90 absolute inset-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-start py-12 px-8 relative z-10 text-white lg:px-0 lg:py-32 lg:items-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-4 lg:text-6xl lg:mb-8">Collaborazioni</h1>
    <p class="text mb-4 lg:text-center lg:mb-4 lg:max-w-screen-md lg:text-lg">La mia avventura online è iniziata per gioco, ma mi ha cambiato la vita. Ho collaborato con brand di livello internazionale e sono diventato ambassador ufficiale di Volvo Trucks Italia, viaggiando in Svezia e in tutta Italia per creare video promozionali e partecipare a eventi.</p>
    <a href="#contact"><button class="translate-x-[2px] w-64 px-4 py-2 bg-brand text-black border-1 border-black shadow-[-4px_4px_0_0_#FFF] transition-all transition-150 hover:translate-x-[-4px] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:shadow-none hover:cursor-pointer active:translate-x-[-4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-none">Collaboriamo</button></a>
  </div>
</section>

<%# CONTACT SECTION %>
<section id="contact" class="relative min-h-[100vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden lg:min-h-[85vh]">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <img src="<%= asset_path("contact.webp") %>" alt="piertutor al telefono" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-[70%_30%] lg:object-[60%_30%]"/>
  
  <!-- Dark overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto w-full px-8 relative z-10 text-white lg:px-0">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between lg:gap-16">
      <!-- Left content - Text -->
      <div class="mb-8 lg:mb-0 lg:max-w-lg lg:flex-shrink-0">
        <h2 class="text-4xl mb-4 lg:text-6xl lg:mb-6">Collaboriamo?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl lg:mb-0">Compila il form e scrivimi una proposta di collaborazione, ti risponderò il prima possibile!</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right content - Form -->
      <div class="w-full lg:max-w-lg lg:flex-shrink-0">
        <%= form_with model: @submission, local: true, class: "space-y-4" do |form| %>
          <!-- Nome Field -->
          <div class="form-control">
            <%= form.text_field :full_name,
                                class: "w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white placeholder-white/70 focus:border-white/50 focus:bg-white/15 focus:outline-none transition-all duration-200",
                                placeholder: "Nome", 
                                required: true %>
          </div>

          <!-- Email Field -->
          <div class="form-control">
            <%= form.email_field :email,
                                 class: "w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white placeholder-white/70 focus:border-white/50 focus:bg-white/15 focus:outline-none transition-all duration-200",
                                 placeholder: "Email", 
                                 required: true %>
          </div>

          <!-- Message Field -->
          <div class="form-control">
            <%= form.text_area :message,
                               class: "w-full px-4 py-3 h-32 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white placeholder-white/70 focus:border-white/50 focus:bg-white/15 focus:outline-none transition-all duration-200 resize-none",
                               placeholder: "Messaggio", 
                               required: true %>
          </div>

          <!-- Submit Button -->
          <div>
            <%= form.submit "Contattami!",
                            class: "translate-x-[2px] w-full px-6 py-3 bg-brand text-black font-semibold border border-black shadow-[-4px_4px_0_0_#FFF] transition-all duration-150 hover:translate-x-[-4px] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:shadow-none cursor-pointer active:translate-x-[-4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-none" %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# FOOTER %>
<footer class="relative bg-white text-black">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-8 py-16 lg:px-0">
    <!-- Logo Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-4xl archivo-black mb-4 lg:text-8xl">@piertutor</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:text-lg">Camionista, Content Creator, Volvo Trucks Ambassador</p>
    </div>
        <!-- Social Links -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-center mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Seguimi</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-4">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/piertutor" class="hover:text-primary transition">Instagram</a>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/gianni.bugno.1" class="hover:text-primary transition">Facebook</a>
            <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@piertutor" class="hover:text-primary transition">TikTok</a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/c/PierantonioDePiccoli" class="hover:text-primary transition">YouTube</a>
          </div>
        </div>
    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
        <p>© 2025 Piertutor. Tutti i diritti riservati.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>